title: "DissolvA: Predictive Dissolution Suite"
abstract: >-
  A free, web-based pharmaceutical dissolution analysis platform: FDA/EMA
  guidance-aligned f1/f2 similarity, 62 kinetic models, bootstrap f2, USP
  monograph compliance checks, and professional reporting.
